item.description:
        &lt;p&gt;Time to time, you would want to empty a log file but keep the filename as such. Instead of deleting and creating the file, you can use the below command:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;cp /dev/null app.log&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

